WEBVTT

01:27.490 --> 01:35.000
[LIVE UP TO YOUR YOUTH]

01:35.500 --> 01:37.930
[Episode 5]

01:40.950 --> 01:42.430
Why are you just standing there?

01:42.430 --> 01:43.530
Get to work!

01:43.710 --> 01:44.400
Go, go, go.

01:45.070 --> 01:46.330
Stop dilly-dallying.

01:48.840 --> 01:50.170
What are you looking at?

01:55.870 --> 01:56.430
Move aside.

01:56.430 --> 01:57.350
Stop right there!

01:57.350 --> 01:58.400
Who allowed you in here?

01:58.400 --> 01:59.430
What are you doing?

01:59.430 --> 02:00.560
What are you measuring here?

02:00.560 --> 02:01.490
Stop measuring!

02:02.000 --> 02:02.870
Measure it properly for me.

02:02.870 --> 02:03.930
What are you doing?

02:04.230 --> 02:05.070
I have something to do here.

02:05.070 --> 02:06.200
I'll be back in a bit.

02:07.910 --> 02:09.210
Be gentle with it.

02:09.710 --> 02:10.310
It's done?

02:10.910 --> 02:11.910
We're measuring.

02:12.190 --> 02:12.650
Big Bro.

02:12.800 --> 02:13.600
Hurry up.

02:13.840 --> 02:15.680
Measure everything clearly.
Note it down carefully.

02:15.680 --> 02:16.490
Write down

02:16.520 --> 02:17.579
the size of each room,

02:17.579 --> 02:18.579
how many beds,

02:18.710 --> 02:19.640
how many tables.

02:19.710 --> 02:20.240
Go on!

02:20.310 --> 02:20.840
Okay, Sir.

02:20.840 --> 02:21.440
Come down.

02:21.520 --> 02:22.520
Who allowed you in here?

02:22.520 --> 02:22.800
Get lost!

02:22.800 --> 02:23.680
Let me tell you...

02:23.680 --> 02:32.620
[Seasons Change Hotel]

02:24.180 --> 02:24.930
Gentlemen,

02:26.280 --> 02:27.130
we have no grudge in the past

02:27.130 --> 02:28.260
and no hatred today.

02:28.800 --> 02:30.079
I don't even know

02:30.079 --> 02:31.300
what kind of act you're putting on here

02:31.300 --> 02:32.690
at my Seasons Change Hotel today.

02:32.690 --> 02:33.460
But whatever it is,

02:33.460 --> 02:34.920
we can talk it over calmly.

02:35.810 --> 02:36.530
In this world,

02:36.530 --> 02:38.790
there are no conflicts we can't resolve.

02:38.810 --> 02:40.590
Maybe it's all a misunderstanding.

02:40.590 --> 02:41.520
Don't you think?

02:41.970 --> 02:44.230
Are you the boss of Seasons Change Hotel?

02:44.690 --> 02:46.150
I, Little Northeasterner,

02:46.150 --> 02:47.130
mean it when I say something.

02:47.130 --> 02:47.660
Alright,

02:50.650 --> 02:52.180
my word carries weight too.

02:57.530 --> 03:00.180
If I finish speaking
and you still can't make the decision,

03:00.180 --> 03:01.150
I'll make sure you end up

03:01.150 --> 03:01.970
drooling in your sleep in your next life.

03:01.970 --> 03:02.700
Understood?

03:04.630 --> 03:06.620
You're telling me I get to decide.

03:07.150 --> 03:08.680
So what exactly do you want?

03:09.120 --> 03:10.970
I'm here to do business with you.

03:13.150 --> 03:14.550
I brought you customers.

03:15.000 --> 03:15.660
Customers?

03:17.079 --> 03:17.500
Sure.

03:18.900 --> 03:21.240
How many people?
And how many days are they staying?

03:21.240 --> 03:21.900
I

03:21.910 --> 03:23.030
just saw your

03:23.030 --> 03:23.810
basement.

03:24.550 --> 03:25.800
I can fill it up

03:25.800 --> 03:26.460
completely

03:27.579 --> 03:28.800
and keep it full for a whole year.

03:28.800 --> 03:29.530
How about that?

03:29.530 --> 03:30.740
Then where will we live?

03:30.740 --> 03:31.740
Shocked now, huh?

03:34.250 --> 03:35.310
You've seen it too.

03:35.410 --> 03:36.460
The basement

03:36.520 --> 03:37.780
is mostly full now.

03:38.300 --> 03:39.370
If it's full,

03:39.620 --> 03:40.280
no problem.

03:41.400 --> 03:42.500
Kick them all out.

03:42.740 --> 03:43.680
-Yeah.
-Yeah.

03:43.710 --> 03:48.700
[Guest Room]

03:43.750 --> 03:44.550
Kick them out.

03:44.579 --> 03:45.380
Why should we?

03:48.530 --> 03:50.860
Let me hear how you plan
to educate people.

03:51.750 --> 03:53.310
I'd like to hear how they educate people.

03:53.310 --> 03:54.440
What are you saying?

03:55.030 --> 03:55.760
Say it again!

03:55.860 --> 03:56.970
Didn't you understand what I said?

03:56.970 --> 03:58.210
-Where do you come from?
-Let's figure out the situation first.

03:58.210 --> 03:58.870
Okay, okay.

04:01.080 --> 04:02.480
Talk to me. Keep talking.

04:05.250 --> 04:06.370
We're working on a project

04:06.370 --> 04:07.400
nearby,

04:07.800 --> 04:10.200
and I need to find a place
for my guys to stay.

04:10.650 --> 04:11.240
I think

04:11.240 --> 04:12.700
your place is pretty good,

04:14.130 --> 04:15.590
so I want them to stay here.

04:16.540 --> 04:18.190
They're not here to
demolish the guesthouse.

04:18.190 --> 04:19.070
They're working on a project

04:19.070 --> 04:20.269
and want to stay here,

04:20.370 --> 04:21.430
not to tear it down.

04:22.120 --> 04:23.320
But I'm really sorry.

04:24.270 --> 04:25.660
My guests are all regulars.

04:25.660 --> 04:26.540
I can't just kick them out

04:26.540 --> 04:28.270
-because of you.
-How dare you!

04:32.500 --> 04:34.030
Don't think that your beard

04:34.180 --> 04:34.860
scares me.

04:35.260 --> 04:37.280
If you dare lay a finger on me today,

04:37.930 --> 04:39.460
I'll call my friend Tang

04:39.740 --> 04:40.930
at the police station

04:40.930 --> 04:41.740
and have him

04:41.740 --> 04:42.860
deal with you properly.

04:42.860 --> 04:43.500
Do you believe me?

04:43.500 --> 04:44.700
I've got a bad temper!

04:53.810 --> 04:54.670
What happened?

04:55.540 --> 04:56.500
There's going to be a fight.

04:56.500 --> 04:57.210
What? What?

04:57.480 --> 04:58.390
My bad temper!

04:58.510 --> 05:00.110
You're asking for a beating!

05:01.070 --> 05:01.680
Enough.

05:02.780 --> 05:03.840
What are you doing?

05:05.330 --> 05:06.990
They can't really pluck them.

05:12.490 --> 05:14.660
You have relatives
at the police station, huh?

05:14.660 --> 05:16.720
If I didn't have someone watching my back,

05:16.720 --> 05:18.720
would I dare do business in Beijing?

05:19.620 --> 05:21.700
We pay to stay here too.

05:22.190 --> 05:23.870
We'll pay whatever they pay.

05:24.560 --> 05:26.210
I'll even add extra for each room.

05:26.210 --> 05:27.070
How about that?

05:27.120 --> 05:28.720
It's not about adding the money.

05:28.720 --> 05:29.240
These people,

05:29.240 --> 05:30.640
aren't ordinary guests.

05:31.250 --> 05:33.380
They are like my brothers and sisters.

05:33.740 --> 05:34.560
I can't just

05:34.560 --> 05:35.240
throw them out

05:35.240 --> 05:36.430
for a bit more cash!

05:36.580 --> 05:38.040
No amount of money will do.

05:38.060 --> 05:38.930
Yeah, exactly.

05:39.420 --> 05:40.240
That won't do.

05:40.310 --> 05:42.500
Besides, how much more can you add?

05:44.180 --> 05:45.870
I'll add 20 yuan a day per room.

05:47.190 --> 05:47.920
How about it?

05:47.950 --> 05:48.440
Twenty.

05:48.470 --> 05:49.050
Twenty.

05:49.080 --> 05:49.780
Twenty.

05:49.780 --> 05:50.780
Plus 20.

05:51.170 --> 05:51.750
How much?

05:52.130 --> 05:53.560
20 yuan a day per room.

05:57.240 --> 05:58.470
One bed costs 6 yuan.

05:58.500 --> 05:59.600
He adds 20 yuan for a room.

05:59.600 --> 06:02.130
That's several yuan more per bed
than before.

06:03.240 --> 06:04.660
But I can't just

06:04.660 --> 06:05.740
kick everyone out at once.

06:05.740 --> 06:06.350
Look.

06:06.420 --> 06:08.180
If you can't kick them all out at once,

06:08.180 --> 06:09.640
then kick them out slowly.

06:10.130 --> 06:10.860
If you do it quickly,

06:10.860 --> 06:12.270
I'll add another 10 yuan per room.

06:12.270 --> 06:13.070
Is that a deal?

06:13.160 --> 06:13.890
Whether you make this money

06:13.890 --> 06:14.860
is up to you.

06:14.860 --> 06:15.680
Little Northeasterner.

06:15.680 --> 06:16.300
Then where will we live?

06:16.300 --> 06:17.700
Little Northeasterner?

06:18.540 --> 06:19.630
Where are we supposed to live?

06:19.630 --> 06:21.030
Little Northeasterner.

06:22.450 --> 06:23.440
Wait, wait.

06:25.430 --> 06:27.360
If it really doesn't work,
I'll talk to them.

06:27.360 --> 06:27.960
Talk to me!

06:28.300 --> 06:28.630
Wait,

06:29.160 --> 06:30.750
what are you even doing here?

06:30.750 --> 06:32.180
Is it your place to speak here?

06:32.180 --> 06:33.240
Are you the Big Bro?

06:33.390 --> 06:34.240
Are you blind?

06:34.770 --> 06:36.100
My Big Bro is right here.

06:38.420 --> 06:38.880
Big Bro.

06:39.540 --> 06:40.000
Hello.

06:40.330 --> 06:41.330
You've got style.

06:42.010 --> 06:43.100
Are you from Nancheng?

06:43.100 --> 06:44.030
I'm from Xuanwu.

06:45.570 --> 06:46.370
What do you do?

06:46.659 --> 06:47.100
Me?

06:47.860 --> 06:48.870
I play the saxophone.

06:48.870 --> 06:49.600
An artist.

06:49.770 --> 06:51.830
More like the one being played by art.

06:54.810 --> 06:55.950
It's like this.

06:56.159 --> 06:58.140
I've been at Seasons Change Hotel

06:58.450 --> 06:59.850
for almost two years now.

07:00.330 --> 07:01.370
I heard

07:02.120 --> 07:04.120
you're going to tear it down, right?

07:04.510 --> 07:04.950
No.

07:05.190 --> 07:06.010
They're just trying to

07:06.010 --> 07:06.870
kick everyone out.

07:06.870 --> 07:07.930
Kick everyone out?

07:09.540 --> 07:11.140
I treat this place like home,

07:11.300 --> 07:12.480
and I treat the people here

07:12.480 --> 07:13.480
like family.

07:13.800 --> 07:15.360
Forget whether they agree or not—

07:15.360 --> 07:16.300
I won't

07:16.630 --> 07:17.600
allow it.

07:18.130 --> 07:19.240
Right, Mrs. Wang?

07:19.370 --> 07:19.740
Yes!

07:19.770 --> 07:20.500
Right, Mr. Zhao?

07:20.500 --> 07:21.060
Yes!

07:21.180 --> 07:22.250
Who's kicking us out?

07:22.250 --> 07:22.580
Come.

07:23.740 --> 07:24.100
Fine.

07:24.770 --> 07:25.740
Saxophone player,

07:25.740 --> 07:26.770
you've got guts.

07:27.810 --> 07:29.010
I heard that clearly.

07:30.120 --> 07:31.120
I'll count you in.

07:32.010 --> 07:32.620
So what?

07:33.500 --> 07:34.450
Anyone else?

07:36.070 --> 07:37.190
Are we about to hear from

07:37.190 --> 07:38.790
your whole extended family?

07:40.300 --> 07:40.750
Hello.

07:43.659 --> 07:45.190
Come. Come here, come here.

07:50.500 --> 07:51.570
Next time you try to show off,

07:51.570 --> 07:53.630
get your facts straight first, okay?

07:56.220 --> 07:57.150
Nice to meet you.

07:59.480 --> 08:01.250
From your hairstyle,

08:01.250 --> 08:03.240
I'm guessing you're also in the arts?

08:03.240 --> 08:04.040
I'm a painter.

08:05.760 --> 08:07.020
Do you like paintings?

08:07.180 --> 08:08.440
If you like paintings,

08:08.480 --> 08:09.480
I'll give you one.

08:09.690 --> 08:10.560
Once I become famous,

08:10.560 --> 08:12.360
my paintings will be priceless.

08:19.830 --> 08:21.230
What are you laughing at?

08:21.480 --> 08:22.370
My paintings are currently

08:22.370 --> 08:23.210
featured in a

08:23.240 --> 08:24.680
huge art exhibition.

08:24.860 --> 08:25.480
I might just

08:25.480 --> 08:26.940
become famous overnight.

08:28.950 --> 08:29.860
I get it.

08:30.980 --> 08:32.130
You're a fraud?

08:34.890 --> 08:35.240
Fine.

08:36.700 --> 08:37.700
I'll count you in.

08:41.960 --> 08:42.600
Does anyone else at Seasons Change Hotel

08:42.600 --> 08:43.850
still want to speak?

08:52.500 --> 08:53.280
Who?

08:55.370 --> 08:55.940
Zhuang.

09:02.130 --> 09:04.270
Here comes a little Mu Guiying.

09:04.460 --> 09:05.600
You know Mu Guiying;

09:05.960 --> 09:07.550
that means you're someone educated

09:07.550 --> 09:08.460
and polite.

09:09.220 --> 09:10.420
I don't deserve that.

09:12.100 --> 09:13.130
Anyone can stay

09:13.170 --> 09:14.480
at Seasons Change Hotel,

09:14.480 --> 09:16.120
but we've got to be reasonable.

09:16.120 --> 09:17.430
You can't just plant yourself here

09:17.430 --> 09:19.090
and act like you own the place.

09:19.770 --> 09:21.700
Are you saying I'm unreasonable?

09:29.870 --> 09:30.670
What do you do?

09:31.000 --> 09:32.600
It doesn't matter what we do.

09:33.010 --> 09:34.460
As long as we pay the rent,

09:34.860 --> 09:35.620
there's no reason

09:35.620 --> 09:36.510
to kick us out.

09:36.670 --> 09:38.000
Zhuang Zhuang is right.

09:38.250 --> 09:39.450
-Yes.
-You're right.

09:39.860 --> 09:41.250
That makes sense.

09:41.580 --> 09:42.640
Look at that girl's

09:43.280 --> 09:44.500
sharp tongue.

09:45.550 --> 09:47.810
I always tell you guys to read more books,

09:48.250 --> 09:49.510
but none of you listen.

09:51.380 --> 09:52.150
Little girl,

09:53.240 --> 09:54.720
you really can talk.

09:55.460 --> 09:55.990
Alright.

09:57.010 --> 09:57.890
I get it.

09:59.390 --> 10:00.650
I'll count you in, too.

10:15.620 --> 10:17.420
Go ahead, laugh all you want.

10:17.670 --> 10:18.800
Big Bro, I was wrong.

10:26.940 --> 10:27.650
Speak!

10:28.690 --> 10:29.480
Go on!

10:38.640 --> 10:40.530
Those guys are like bandits.

10:40.950 --> 10:42.150
They all have thick beards.

10:42.150 --> 10:43.350
They're terrifying.

10:44.240 --> 10:45.170
What should I do?

10:45.750 --> 10:47.150
Tang, you have to help me.

10:47.980 --> 10:48.680
Look.

10:48.910 --> 10:50.460
They want to stay in your place.

10:50.460 --> 10:52.320
Whether you let them or not is your call.

10:52.320 --> 10:54.030
I said no, but they insist.

10:54.360 --> 10:55.320
Does your big boss,

10:55.320 --> 10:55.980
your uncle,

10:56.240 --> 10:57.170
know about this?

10:59.210 --> 11:00.290
I haven't had time to tell him yet—

11:00.290 --> 11:01.910
that's why we called you here.

11:01.910 --> 11:02.440
Alright.

11:02.910 --> 11:03.490
You

11:03.770 --> 11:04.550
should go discuss it

11:04.550 --> 11:05.350
with your boss

11:05.670 --> 11:06.410
and see whether this deal

11:06.410 --> 11:07.810
is going to be done or not.

11:08.080 --> 11:08.500
Also,

11:08.960 --> 11:09.720
regarding those people,

11:09.720 --> 11:10.960
if they do anything

11:10.960 --> 11:12.160
other than business,

11:12.600 --> 11:14.270
call the station immediately.

11:14.270 --> 11:15.930
We will intervene right away.

11:16.480 --> 11:18.010
Alright, that's it for now.

11:20.240 --> 11:21.510
These guys are basically thugs—

11:21.510 --> 11:24.000
crude, vulgar,

11:24.440 --> 11:25.840
completely unbearable.

11:27.320 --> 11:29.270
I've been wanting to hit him
for a long time.

11:29.270 --> 11:31.060
I... I almost did too.

11:31.120 --> 11:32.450
I held myself back,

11:33.150 --> 11:34.700
then I thought

11:34.910 --> 11:36.040
that wouldn't work.

11:36.510 --> 11:38.500
If we strike first,

11:38.500 --> 11:40.430
they'll have leverage against us.

11:43.960 --> 11:45.440
Didn't you pick up a brick today?

11:45.440 --> 11:46.700
Why did you put it back?

11:47.120 --> 11:47.950
I told you.

11:48.030 --> 11:50.530
If we strike first,
they'll have leverage against us.

11:50.530 --> 11:51.010
Zongbao,

11:51.010 --> 11:52.360
didn't you just go to the restroom?

11:52.360 --> 11:52.940
Did you fall in?

11:52.940 --> 11:54.080
I didn't see you the whole time.

11:54.080 --> 11:54.480
What?

11:55.030 --> 11:57.340
I was at the stairwell entrance.

11:57.550 --> 11:58.750
Those ladies

11:58.750 --> 11:59.840
were shaking with fear.

11:59.840 --> 12:01.590
I was there comforting them.

12:02.000 --> 12:02.940
Were you comforting them,

12:02.940 --> 12:03.510
or were you there

12:03.510 --> 12:04.840
shaking right along with them?

12:04.840 --> 12:05.120
I...

12:05.600 --> 12:07.120
I even grabbed a mop.

12:07.150 --> 12:08.350
I was ready to charge.

12:09.270 --> 12:10.400
For mopping floors?

12:10.440 --> 12:11.550
Mopping.

12:12.390 --> 12:14.080
They've already pulled knives,

12:14.080 --> 12:15.320
and we're all just people

12:15.320 --> 12:17.440
living on the edge here anyway.

12:18.120 --> 12:20.310
Are we really?

12:20.440 --> 12:21.240
Who wasn't?

12:27.320 --> 12:28.310
Who wasn't?

12:29.870 --> 12:30.930
Alright, alright.

12:31.550 --> 12:32.550
Say no more.

12:33.750 --> 12:35.010
If they want us to move,

12:35.620 --> 12:36.750
then we move.

12:37.240 --> 12:38.900
Tomorrow we'll quickly find a

12:38.960 --> 12:39.890
cheaper place

12:40.440 --> 12:42.630
and try to stay together.

12:43.440 --> 12:44.480
You guys can look for a place if you want.

12:44.480 --> 12:45.340
I'm not moving.

12:46.740 --> 12:48.000
That guy surnamed Feng

12:48.370 --> 12:49.630
is a ruthless one.

12:50.580 --> 12:53.260
A wise man knows when to yield.

12:56.290 --> 12:56.980
Tie,

12:57.030 --> 12:58.080
you can't treat my place

12:58.080 --> 12:59.210
like your workplace

12:59.630 --> 13:00.960
and show up on time every day.

13:00.960 --> 13:02.630
Who can stand that?

13:04.080 --> 13:06.340
Give us a chance to breathe,

13:06.360 --> 13:07.270
let us...

13:07.890 --> 13:08.340
Bro,

13:08.670 --> 13:09.370
I just took the brothers

13:09.370 --> 13:10.440
for another look around.

13:10.440 --> 13:11.040
This place

13:11.200 --> 13:12.460
is perfect for us to live in.

13:12.460 --> 13:14.320
The brothers are all super happy.

13:14.500 --> 13:15.100
Do you like it?

13:15.100 --> 13:15.500
Yes.

13:15.530 --> 13:16.360
Then we'll stay here.

13:16.360 --> 13:16.960
Stay here.

13:16.980 --> 13:18.790
You'll even get married here
and make it your wedding home.

13:18.790 --> 13:20.000
What exactly do you want

13:20.000 --> 13:21.060
to do with my place?

13:21.440 --> 13:22.300
Just stay here.

13:23.390 --> 13:25.290
There are so many shops

13:25.320 --> 13:26.170
and guesthouses all around—

13:26.170 --> 13:27.750
why did you choose us?

13:27.750 --> 13:28.130
What's so special

13:28.130 --> 13:29.480
about our place?

13:29.700 --> 13:30.900
The location is good,

13:31.120 --> 13:32.130
the size is right,

13:32.510 --> 13:33.370
and it's cheap.

13:33.480 --> 13:34.590
That's low cost,

13:34.620 --> 13:35.350
high return.

13:36.100 --> 13:37.160
Most importantly,

13:37.480 --> 13:38.630
I like you.

13:39.000 --> 13:39.460
Really.

13:40.380 --> 13:41.290
Don't be a coward.

13:41.290 --> 13:41.750
I just like you

13:41.750 --> 13:42.820
stiffening your neck like that.

13:42.820 --> 13:44.350
Come on. Stiffen your neck.

13:46.240 --> 13:47.520
Tie,

13:48.270 --> 13:50.340
stop teasing me.

13:50.910 --> 13:51.310
You...

13:52.200 --> 13:52.760
Just...

13:53.240 --> 13:54.670
Let me off the hook, will you?

13:54.670 --> 13:55.800
Let you off the hook?

13:57.390 --> 13:59.180
I'd need to have a hook first.

14:04.220 --> 14:05.750
I'll tell you one more time.

14:06.580 --> 14:07.710
We are staying here.

14:08.410 --> 14:09.540
We are staying here!

14:10.580 --> 14:11.690
Do you understand?

14:14.010 --> 14:15.340
Stop talking nonsense.

14:17.870 --> 14:20.530
-Don't you scare when he acts like this?
-Come here.

14:20.530 --> 14:21.330
Go over there!

14:24.010 --> 14:25.410
Little Northeasterner,

14:26.440 --> 14:27.440
let me tell you,

14:28.650 --> 14:30.250
I don't like to bully people.

14:31.050 --> 14:32.320
Seeing how aggrieved you look

14:32.320 --> 14:33.450
makes my heart ache.

14:34.170 --> 14:34.630
Really.

14:35.650 --> 14:36.510
How about this?

14:36.720 --> 14:38.050
Let bygones be bygones.

14:38.650 --> 14:39.620
From now on,

14:39.620 --> 14:41.000
I'll give you three days

14:41.240 --> 14:42.430
to drive them away.

14:42.870 --> 14:43.530
Okay?

14:44.290 --> 14:46.520
How can I kick them out, Tie?

14:46.770 --> 14:48.250
They've already paid rent.

14:48.250 --> 14:49.410
They won't leave just because I say so.

14:49.410 --> 14:50.770
What can I do if they won't leave?

14:50.770 --> 14:51.500
Then do this.

14:51.770 --> 14:53.050
Call them all out.

14:53.700 --> 14:54.740
If you can't handle it, I can.

14:54.740 --> 14:55.500
I'll talk to them.

14:55.500 --> 14:55.940
Okay?

15:02.410 --> 15:04.140
Are you pulling a long face now?

15:04.440 --> 15:04.960
Zhuang,

15:05.180 --> 15:06.370
take the brothers

15:06.580 --> 15:07.670
downstairs and round everyone up.

15:07.670 --> 15:08.530
See who is here

15:08.530 --> 15:09.360
and call them all over.

15:09.360 --> 15:10.420
Then tell them

15:10.510 --> 15:11.510
Little Northeasterner

15:11.510 --> 15:12.810
is going to give them money.

15:12.810 --> 15:13.670
Okay, Brother.

15:14.370 --> 15:15.040
Come back.

15:16.870 --> 15:18.070
Go back and stay put.

15:22.740 --> 15:24.350
You just keep stalling here.

15:25.000 --> 15:26.800
I have plenty of ways to kill you.

15:29.270 --> 15:30.800
Why are there so few people?

15:31.340 --> 15:33.070
Why are there only a few people?

15:34.720 --> 15:36.580
Everyone staying here is decent—

15:36.670 --> 15:38.330
they go to work during the day.

15:38.720 --> 15:39.860
There aren't that many unemployed loafers

15:39.860 --> 15:40.550
or vagrants.

15:40.550 --> 15:41.840
Who are you talking about?

15:41.840 --> 15:42.840
Did I mention you?

15:42.840 --> 15:44.840
Don't assume I'm talking about you.

15:45.390 --> 15:46.400
Don't be afraid.

15:47.080 --> 15:47.880
I've been here

15:48.390 --> 15:49.340
several times,

15:49.720 --> 15:50.580
and you all know

15:51.030 --> 15:52.030
what I'm here for.

15:53.440 --> 15:54.530
Today, I want to properly

15:54.530 --> 15:55.530
talk with you all.

15:55.720 --> 15:56.120
Okay?

15:58.550 --> 15:59.480
Can you move out?

15:59.510 --> 16:00.270
Why should we?

16:00.270 --> 16:01.200
We've paid.

16:03.320 --> 16:04.240
Then if Little Northeasterner

16:04.240 --> 16:05.360
refunds your rent

16:05.390 --> 16:07.030
and gives you an extra half month's rent,

16:07.030 --> 16:07.830
will you move?

16:08.320 --> 16:09.480
Why should I pay an extra

16:09.480 --> 16:10.540
half month's rent?

16:11.360 --> 16:12.880
Okay. I... I'll move.

16:16.320 --> 16:16.920
Thank you.

16:18.550 --> 16:19.680
What about you, Sir?

16:20.720 --> 16:21.920
I'll move. I'll move.

16:23.360 --> 16:23.960
Thank you.

16:25.840 --> 16:27.040
What about you, miss?

16:27.120 --> 16:27.720
I'll move.

16:27.860 --> 16:28.990
I'll move tomorrow.

16:29.730 --> 16:31.370
I'll go back and pack in a bit.

16:33.050 --> 16:33.480
Move.

16:33.830 --> 16:34.940
I'll move right away.

16:34.940 --> 16:36.160
I'll move tomorrow.

16:37.630 --> 16:38.430
It's settled.

16:39.720 --> 16:40.780
See? It's settled.

16:40.840 --> 16:41.970
Talk to them nicely.

16:44.120 --> 16:44.910
Go back with them

16:44.910 --> 16:46.310
and pack up their things.

16:46.600 --> 16:47.950
Thank you.

16:48.030 --> 16:48.840
-Okay, brother.
-Thank you.

16:48.840 --> 16:49.460
Let's go.

16:49.460 --> 16:50.320
-Let's go.
-Let's go.

16:50.320 --> 16:50.640
Go!

16:50.660 --> 16:51.860
-Let's go.
-Let's go.

16:55.750 --> 16:56.540
You...

16:56.840 --> 16:58.390
You should talk to those artsy,

16:58.390 --> 16:59.000
talkative ones

16:59.000 --> 16:59.930
the same way too,

17:00.200 --> 17:00.730
alright?

17:02.790 --> 17:05.250
If it still doesn't work out,
come back to me.

17:05.550 --> 17:06.550
Keep your head up.

17:08.349 --> 17:09.660
That's how I like you.

17:19.010 --> 17:19.480
Uncle,

17:19.980 --> 17:21.109
let me fill your cup.

17:22.609 --> 17:23.829
Anyway, at Seasons Change Hotel,

17:23.829 --> 17:24.960
you're the big boss.

17:26.319 --> 17:27.980
I really have no other way now.

17:28.420 --> 17:29.820
Please tell me what to do.

17:30.250 --> 17:31.310
Is there a problem?

17:32.500 --> 17:34.700
Didn't they already raise the room fee?

17:35.030 --> 17:36.080
Remember,

17:36.350 --> 17:38.550
we're running a business to make money.

17:38.880 --> 17:41.180
An extra 20 per room per day—

17:41.290 --> 17:42.460
multiply that by a month,

17:42.460 --> 17:43.830
then a year. Do the math.

17:45.180 --> 17:46.970
That makes sense.

17:47.330 --> 17:48.770
But these regular guests—

17:48.770 --> 17:50.190
I brought them in one
by one from the train station

17:50.190 --> 17:50.980
and long-distance bus station

17:50.980 --> 17:52.570
myself.

17:52.810 --> 17:53.810
I've been maintaining these relationships
day after day,

17:53.810 --> 17:55.830
and that's how they became regulars.

17:55.830 --> 17:57.240
If I kick them all out like this,

17:57.240 --> 17:58.830
I just can't feel right about it.

17:58.830 --> 18:00.050
They'll be hurt too.

18:00.350 --> 18:00.830
So,

18:02.140 --> 18:04.000
you'd leave the money on the table

18:04.200 --> 18:05.530
and make me sad instead?

18:06.440 --> 18:06.980
You just

18:07.070 --> 18:08.360
go talk to everyone.

18:08.740 --> 18:10.850
Refund or compensate them however needed.

18:10.850 --> 18:11.570
Hurry up and clear the rooms

18:11.570 --> 18:12.570
for these guests.

18:13.180 --> 18:13.440
Look,

18:13.440 --> 18:14.430
listen to me.

18:14.900 --> 18:17.230
I hired you as the manager

18:17.380 --> 18:19.750
to help me run the place and make money,

18:20.720 --> 18:21.900
not to play the loyal brother

18:21.900 --> 18:23.630
and get emotional with people.

18:26.420 --> 18:29.400
[Guest Room]

18:34.900 --> 18:37.050
Which bastard pulled the switch?

18:38.320 --> 18:39.110
It's so hot.

18:39.110 --> 18:39.960
This power cut...

18:39.960 --> 18:41.560
I never said I wouldn't move.

18:42.850 --> 18:44.660
Little Northeasterner,
are you actually in charge or not?

18:44.660 --> 18:45.710
It's so hot.

18:50.480 --> 18:51.770
Is there no end to this?

18:52.530 --> 18:53.570
No warning for the power outage,

18:53.570 --> 18:55.100
and now the water's cut too.

18:55.790 --> 18:57.420
I just put shampoo in my hair.

18:57.800 --> 18:58.640
Line up.

18:57.850 --> 18:58.780
[Seasons Change Hotel]

18:58.780 --> 19:03.020
[Emergency Water Supply]

18:59.530 --> 19:00.160
Make room.

19:00.570 --> 19:02.130
The neighborhood committee
sent water for everyone.

19:02.130 --> 19:02.730
Over here.

19:12.090 --> 19:13.130
Bring the booze.

19:14.590 --> 19:15.290
After tonight,

19:15.290 --> 19:17.600
we're moving to Seasons Change Hotel.

19:17.700 --> 19:18.270
Is that good?

19:18.270 --> 19:18.880
Good!

19:18.880 --> 19:20.390
I found a place for you.

19:20.530 --> 19:21.130
Bottom up!

19:21.510 --> 19:22.910
-CBottom up.
-Bottom up.

19:23.960 --> 19:25.020
Mrs. Xu, Mrs. Wang,

19:25.440 --> 19:26.790
are you leaving today too?

19:26.790 --> 19:28.050
Luo, here are the keys.

19:29.240 --> 19:29.770
Okay.

19:30.200 --> 19:30.880
If you forgot anything,

19:30.880 --> 19:31.920
just give me a call.

19:31.920 --> 19:33.110
I'll mail it all to you.

19:33.110 --> 19:34.350
Luo, you stay safe too.

19:34.350 --> 19:35.070
Don't worry.

19:35.070 --> 19:36.670
They can't do anything to me.

19:36.680 --> 19:37.290
Take care, sis.

19:37.290 --> 19:37.620
Okay.

19:38.740 --> 19:39.560
Bye.

19:41.920 --> 19:44.160
Seasons Change Hotel will always be there.

19:44.160 --> 19:44.810
Lei.

19:45.680 --> 19:46.280
Thank you.

19:47.550 --> 19:48.530
Mr. Xu.

19:48.690 --> 19:50.070
Have you packed your things?

19:50.070 --> 19:51.940
[Guest Room]

19:50.480 --> 19:51.410
What's the rush?

19:51.980 --> 19:53.340
You should be in a rush.

19:53.350 --> 20:02.670
[Guest Room]

19:55.580 --> 19:57.980
I've been thinking about something today.

19:58.690 --> 20:00.240
Do you really believe that guy Feng Tieyou

20:00.240 --> 20:01.700
will actually pay the rent

20:01.920 --> 20:02.650
he promised?

20:04.440 --> 20:05.170
First of all,

20:06.180 --> 20:07.480
our place

20:07.510 --> 20:08.670
is decent,

20:09.030 --> 20:10.000
but it's not exactly

20:10.000 --> 20:11.430
upscale.

20:11.500 --> 20:13.100
With an extra 20 yuan a day,

20:13.750 --> 20:15.610
he could get a proper double room.

20:16.400 --> 20:17.200
Is he a sucker?

20:19.720 --> 20:20.190
Second,

20:21.160 --> 20:22.220
with such a big deal

20:22.640 --> 20:24.110
and so many people involved,

20:24.110 --> 20:25.090
If I were you,

20:25.470 --> 20:26.960
I'd at least ask for a discount.

20:26.960 --> 20:28.810
Discount? I'll break their legs instead.

20:28.810 --> 20:29.450
Exactly.

20:30.460 --> 20:30.860
Third,

20:32.050 --> 20:34.380
if they can't get any advantage on rent,

20:35.290 --> 20:37.140
then they'll try to take advantage

20:37.140 --> 20:38.220
of the rooms instead, right?

20:38.220 --> 20:39.050
What do you mean?

20:39.050 --> 20:40.350
What do I mean?

20:40.420 --> 20:42.740
Upper bunks, lower bunks,
even sleeping on the floor.

20:42.740 --> 20:44.180
They're treating my place
like a sleeper train carriage.

20:44.180 --> 20:44.720
Anyway,

20:45.480 --> 20:46.610
you need to be clear.

20:47.380 --> 20:49.750
No proof, no deal.

20:53.110 --> 20:54.240
See you around, Luo.

20:57.220 --> 20:58.200
Get the hell out of here!

20:58.200 --> 20:58.700
Chen Yan.

20:58.700 --> 20:59.640
Go back to where you came from.

20:59.640 --> 21:00.880
Chen Yan, who wants your junk?

21:00.880 --> 21:01.350
Take it back.

21:01.350 --> 21:02.610
Listen to me, Chen Yan.

21:03.110 --> 21:04.770
Go back to where you came from.

21:08.270 --> 21:08.800
Chen Yan.

21:08.900 --> 21:09.560
Feng Tieyou

21:09.610 --> 21:10.920
really knows he was wrong this time.

21:10.920 --> 21:12.180
Just see him, will you?

21:12.330 --> 21:13.250
Every day now,

21:13.400 --> 21:14.730
he doesn't eat or sleep.

21:14.790 --> 21:15.850
If you keep this up,

21:15.850 --> 21:16.450
this guy is

21:16.550 --> 21:17.890
gonna kick the bucket.

21:18.010 --> 21:18.740
Shut up.

21:18.940 --> 21:19.820
Who is your sister-in-law?

21:19.820 --> 21:21.020
We divorced ages ago.

21:21.090 --> 21:21.630
That's great.

21:21.630 --> 21:22.980
That way he can make
a contribution to society.

21:22.980 --> 21:23.380
You...

21:25.350 --> 21:26.100
Xu.

21:26.960 --> 21:27.890
Sis, you're busy. Go ahead.

21:27.890 --> 21:28.620
I'm not busy.

21:28.660 --> 21:29.580
Come, let me see.

21:29.580 --> 21:30.940
What do you have in your hand?

21:30.940 --> 21:32.240
It's nothing. Just some dried clams.

21:32.240 --> 21:33.850
A specialty from my hometown.

21:33.850 --> 21:34.440
That's wonderful!

21:34.440 --> 21:35.770
I just love dried clams.

21:36.180 --> 21:37.030
I'm telling you,

21:37.030 --> 21:38.050
get the hell out of here.

21:38.050 --> 21:39.030
If I see you again,

21:39.030 --> 21:41.090
he will never see me in this lifetime.

21:41.330 --> 21:42.640
How is setting up the stall going?

21:42.640 --> 21:42.980
Pretty good.

21:42.980 --> 21:44.480
That's why I came
specifically to thank you.

21:44.480 --> 21:45.460
No need to be polite.

21:45.460 --> 21:46.720
Just let me know if you need anything.

21:46.720 --> 21:47.320
Alright, go on.

21:47.320 --> 21:49.050
I'll get back to work then, Sis.

21:50.050 --> 21:50.510
So nice.

21:52.720 --> 21:53.250
Get lost!

21:56.180 --> 21:58.090
Room rates 50% off?

21:56.350 --> 21:59.120
[Cash and payment method]

21:58.500 --> 21:58.960
Right.

21:59.500 --> 22:00.430
No need to shout.

22:00.500 --> 22:01.670
I wrote it. I know.

22:05.350 --> 22:06.570
Didn't you say before

22:06.570 --> 22:08.570
that you'd pay extra for every room?

22:09.250 --> 22:09.880
Now you...

22:10.550 --> 22:11.570
I kicked everyone out,

22:11.570 --> 22:12.700
and now you want a discount?

22:12.700 --> 22:13.700
Did I say that?

22:14.090 --> 22:15.380
Bro, you did say that.

22:18.920 --> 22:20.120
Do I keep my word?

22:20.220 --> 22:21.950
That depends on your mood, Bro.

22:25.900 --> 22:27.760
I'm in a really bad mood right now.

22:29.700 --> 22:31.300
I've booked the whole place.

22:31.740 --> 22:33.000
If I buy a truckload of cabbage,

22:33.000 --> 22:34.730
shouldn't there be a discount?

22:35.850 --> 22:37.380
Just sign it already.

22:38.440 --> 22:39.570
How many people are you planning

22:39.570 --> 22:40.570
to put in one room?

22:41.460 --> 22:42.500
I knew you kid

22:42.500 --> 22:43.590
had a sharp brain.

22:44.420 --> 22:45.610
I've booked the whole house.

22:45.610 --> 22:47.000
I can stuff as many people in as I want.

22:47.000 --> 22:47.590
Right?

22:48.850 --> 22:49.860
Tie,

22:50.030 --> 22:51.590
you can't do this.

22:51.610 --> 22:53.060
Then how should I do it?

22:53.790 --> 22:54.460
If you do this,

22:54.460 --> 22:56.240
I definitely can't agree.

22:56.530 --> 22:57.530
Northeasterner,

22:58.500 --> 22:59.960
you just said it yourself.

23:01.240 --> 23:02.990
The money you lost

23:03.160 --> 23:04.330
from refunding the rooms,

23:04.330 --> 23:05.720
adds up to quite a lot, doesn't it?

23:05.720 --> 23:06.330
Right?

23:06.740 --> 23:08.640
And your reputation for kicking out guests

23:08.640 --> 23:09.770
has already spread.

23:09.850 --> 23:11.580
If I don't take over this place,

23:11.610 --> 23:12.440
will the people living here now

23:12.440 --> 23:13.260
feel at ease?

23:13.420 --> 23:14.590
They'll definitely look for a new place.

23:14.590 --> 23:15.270
Once they find a new place,

23:15.270 --> 23:16.210
they'll pack up and roll out.

23:16.210 --> 23:16.660
Right?

23:17.290 --> 23:17.900
When that happens,

23:17.900 --> 23:20.030
the old ones leave and no new ones come.

23:20.350 --> 23:21.950
Whether it's a loss or a gain,

23:22.200 --> 23:23.460
weigh it in your heart.

23:24.000 --> 23:25.000
Isn't that right?

23:28.010 --> 23:28.750
You don't

23:29.810 --> 23:31.070
need to think about it.

23:31.500 --> 23:32.100
Just sign.

23:35.570 --> 23:36.570
This contract

23:36.920 --> 23:38.410
is out of my hands.

23:42.140 --> 23:42.610
Didn't you say

23:42.610 --> 23:44.920
you were in charge of
Seasons Change Hotel?

23:44.920 --> 23:45.960
Are you playing me?

23:45.960 --> 23:47.240
I may be the manager,

23:48.140 --> 23:48.880
but this inn

23:49.110 --> 23:50.310
doesn't belong to me.

23:52.160 --> 23:53.760
I'm going to check the rooms.

23:54.720 --> 23:56.250
Are you trying to push your luck?

23:56.250 --> 23:57.250
You want to hit me?

23:57.270 --> 23:57.930
Fine.

23:58.310 --> 23:59.560
If you hit me today,

24:00.180 --> 24:01.570
then this becomes a police matter—

24:01.570 --> 24:02.290
and I'll be saved the trouble.

24:02.290 --> 24:03.250
Come on.

24:04.530 --> 24:05.010
Look,

24:05.010 --> 24:05.740
stop trying to scare me

24:05.740 --> 24:07.270
with that police relative.

24:08.480 --> 24:09.240
Business

24:09.700 --> 24:11.100
is about mutual consent.

24:11.260 --> 24:12.070
If you weren't willing,

24:12.070 --> 24:13.730
would we have gotten this far?

24:17.590 --> 24:19.790
I'm afraid the longer you drag this out,

24:20.750 --> 24:21.990
the more you'll lose.

24:22.330 --> 24:22.970
Right?

24:24.050 --> 24:25.050
Hurry up and sign.

24:26.160 --> 24:27.560
Call me when you're done.

24:38.500 --> 24:42.290
♪ Where are you from? ♪

24:42.370 --> 24:43.030
Sis.

24:42.460 --> 24:44.180
♪ My... ♪

24:44.420 --> 24:45.400
Xu.

24:45.480 --> 24:46.400
What brings you here?

24:46.400 --> 24:47.770
How are things with you and Zhuang Zhuang?

24:47.770 --> 24:49.500
We're good. Everything's fine.

24:49.500 --> 24:51.010
I wanted to ask you something.

24:51.010 --> 24:51.850
Do you remember

24:51.850 --> 24:53.850
the dried clams I brought you last time?

24:53.850 --> 24:55.550
I was just about to ask you about that.

24:55.550 --> 24:56.700
Those dried clams were delicious.

24:56.700 --> 24:57.460
Do you have any more?

24:57.460 --> 24:58.200
Yes, I do.

24:58.240 --> 24:59.010
I'll bring some over later.

24:59.010 --> 24:59.510
Okay.

25:00.600 --> 25:02.030
I wanted to ask…

25:02.190 --> 25:03.750
Was there a guy with a big beard that day?

25:03.750 --> 25:05.280
Is he someone you know, sis?

25:11.900 --> 25:12.630
No, he isn't.

25:18.090 --> 25:19.270
You're a grown man.

25:19.610 --> 25:21.090
You're snooping around now?

25:21.090 --> 25:23.110
Sis, I'm not snooping.

25:23.500 --> 25:24.360
It's like this.

25:24.400 --> 25:25.270
A construction team came

25:25.270 --> 25:26.240
to the small hostel

25:26.240 --> 25:27.810
where Zhuang Zhuang and I stay.

25:27.810 --> 25:28.850
They insisted on staying there.

25:28.850 --> 25:29.850
They want to kick out

25:29.850 --> 25:30.960
all the previous guests.

25:30.960 --> 25:32.400
It's totally unreasonable.

25:32.400 --> 25:33.530
These past two days,

25:33.700 --> 25:35.570
they cut off the water and power.

25:36.720 --> 25:38.550
Many guests were afraid of trouble,

25:38.550 --> 25:39.700
so they already left.

25:39.700 --> 25:40.820
But I'm young.

25:41.220 --> 25:42.350
I just don't believe

25:42.530 --> 25:43.920
they can do anything to me.

25:43.920 --> 25:45.450
We live in a society of laws.

25:46.050 --> 25:47.050
That bearded guy.

25:47.050 --> 25:47.700
That bearded guy

25:47.700 --> 25:49.500
is with the construction team too.

25:49.500 --> 25:50.660
I was wondering if you

25:50.660 --> 25:51.510
knew him,

25:51.510 --> 25:52.240
could you...

25:52.400 --> 25:53.930
could you put in a good word?

25:55.850 --> 25:56.440
Xu.

25:57.640 --> 25:58.500
Let me tell you.

25:59.590 --> 26:00.260
About this,

26:01.110 --> 26:02.510
they really went too far.

26:03.960 --> 26:04.650
I know.

26:05.090 --> 26:07.460
It hasn't been easy
for you and Zhuang Zhuang.

26:07.460 --> 26:08.860
But I can't get involved.

26:09.960 --> 26:10.640
Besides,

26:11.530 --> 26:12.470
Beijing is huge.

26:14.420 --> 26:15.680
You can live anywhere.

26:17.220 --> 26:18.330
If you come here for business,

26:18.330 --> 26:19.530
we'll talk business.

26:20.290 --> 26:21.620
If you run into trouble,

26:21.940 --> 26:22.870
I'll still help.

26:24.330 --> 26:26.310
But if you insist on bringing him up,

26:26.310 --> 26:27.840
let's pretend we never met.

26:31.610 --> 26:35.330
♪ Like a butterfly ♪

26:35.850 --> 26:39.480
♪ Flying into my window ♪

26:40.960 --> 26:41.830
Take care.

26:43.680 --> 26:44.380
Luo.

26:45.330 --> 26:46.290
Here's your key.

26:50.810 --> 26:52.020
Call me when you get there.

26:52.020 --> 26:52.590
Will do.

26:52.400 --> 26:56.060
[The rights and obligations
of both parties]

26:54.070 --> 26:55.620
Let's not be strangers.

27:01.940 --> 27:02.740
Mr. Xu.

27:04.140 --> 27:05.680
How did you know

27:05.750 --> 27:07.210
they'd try to underpay me?

27:07.410 --> 27:07.910
And...

27:08.640 --> 27:09.810
How did you guess

27:09.830 --> 27:10.610
they'd make people sleep in

27:10.610 --> 27:11.280
bunk beds?

27:13.850 --> 27:15.670
Whichever character you write,

27:15.790 --> 27:17.750
you have to play that role.

27:18.500 --> 27:19.270
You have to follow

27:19.270 --> 27:20.600
that character's logic

27:20.740 --> 27:22.140
to think things through.

27:22.720 --> 27:23.660
This is called

27:24.070 --> 27:25.930
putting yourself in their shoes.

27:27.980 --> 27:29.640
I really underestimated you.

27:31.960 --> 27:32.470
Fine.

27:34.900 --> 27:36.760
I'm definitely not signing this.

27:37.310 --> 27:38.900
I'd like to see what he can do to me.

27:38.900 --> 27:39.910
If he dares to touch me,

27:39.320 --> 27:41.780
[Guest Room]

27:40.380 --> 27:40.980
I'll get Tang

27:40.980 --> 27:41.880
to handcuff them.

27:41.880 --> 27:42.960
Fine.

27:43.770 --> 27:45.810
Then you've got a feud on your hands.

27:45.830 --> 27:48.370
They have plenty of ways to mess with you.

27:48.940 --> 27:50.140
Then what should I do?

27:50.380 --> 27:51.240
I know it's a trap.

27:51.240 --> 27:52.840
Am I supposed to just jump in?

27:52.980 --> 27:54.840
I might actually have a solution.

27:55.660 --> 27:56.590
What's the plan?

27:59.500 --> 28:00.810
Little Northeasterner.

28:00.810 --> 28:05.510
[Guest Room]

28:02.200 --> 28:02.660
Mr. Tao.

28:02.690 --> 28:04.030
I've got a plan

28:04.750 --> 28:06.410
for the Seasons Change Hotel.

28:10.850 --> 28:11.560
What plan?

28:12.290 --> 28:13.550
I know that because of

28:13.550 --> 28:14.740
the contract,

28:14.790 --> 28:16.050
you're in a tough spot.

28:16.050 --> 28:17.200
Leave it to Room 108.

28:17.460 --> 28:18.270
But Room 108

28:18.470 --> 28:19.930
has nothing to do with him.

28:22.250 --> 28:23.850
Stop keeping me in suspense.

28:23.850 --> 28:25.270
What is it? Tell me.

28:25.270 --> 28:26.220
I'm dying to know.

28:26.220 --> 28:28.030
Do you know why Guo didn’t show up

28:28.030 --> 28:28.970
when that Feng

28:29.590 --> 28:31.010
came over?

28:32.110 --> 28:32.740
Why?

28:33.750 --> 28:34.950
Let's step aside.

28:35.270 --> 28:36.420
Walls have ears.

28:36.720 --> 28:38.310
What's the plan? Just tell me.

28:36.860 --> 28:41.810
[Guest Room]

28:38.550 --> 28:40.920
Let's talk inside. Walls have ears.

28:43.110 --> 28:44.510
Section Chief Wang should be on his way.

28:44.510 --> 28:45.070
Today,

28:45.070 --> 28:46.510
he has a very important meeting.

28:46.510 --> 28:47.310
He mentioned earlier

28:47.310 --> 28:48.940
that he might be a little late today.

28:48.940 --> 28:50.460
So is he coming or not?

28:50.720 --> 28:51.350
He is.

28:51.810 --> 28:53.470
He's a leader. Just wait a bit.

28:53.920 --> 28:55.270
This dump of yours

28:55.980 --> 28:57.310
is actually hosting a big shot?

28:57.310 --> 28:58.030
Tie,

28:58.220 --> 28:59.690
this isn't just some dump.

28:59.920 --> 29:01.240
Not just any hostel

29:01.240 --> 29:02.990
can open in this area.

29:03.200 --> 29:04.640
Luogu Hutong.

29:05.460 --> 29:06.590
This Section Chief Wang

29:06.590 --> 29:08.740
grew up playing with my dad.

29:08.740 --> 29:10.580
My dad helped him get where he is.

29:10.850 --> 29:11.710
Technically,

29:12.090 --> 29:13.690
I should call him Uncle Wang.

29:14.450 --> 29:15.510
You two keep chatting.

29:15.510 --> 29:17.040
I'll go welcome Uncle Wang.

29:18.720 --> 29:20.680
-Let me pick up Uncle Wang.
-His neighbor.

29:20.680 --> 29:22.530
-He watched him grow up.
-You’ve already...

29:22.530 --> 29:23.460
Talked big.

29:23.500 --> 29:24.310
Don't poke me.

29:24.350 --> 29:25.050
What?

29:27.240 --> 29:29.300
It's expensive. What if you break it?

29:30.460 --> 29:32.190
I've already set up the dinner.

29:34.290 --> 29:35.550
If he doesn't show up,

29:36.670 --> 29:38.200
it's going to be hilarious.

29:39.440 --> 29:40.300
It's not funny.

29:40.350 --> 29:40.790
Don't.

29:41.380 --> 29:42.220
I'm telling you.

29:42.220 --> 29:43.850
Today is serious.

29:44.770 --> 29:46.100
It's serious business.

29:48.380 --> 29:48.980
He's here.

29:49.220 --> 29:49.940
Uncle Wang is here.

29:49.940 --> 29:50.770
Section Chief Wang is here.

29:50.770 --> 29:51.610
Hurry.

30:08.750 --> 30:09.680
-Section Chief Wang.
-Uncle Wang. Uncle Wang.

30:09.680 --> 30:10.590
I heard
the District Construction Committee

30:10.590 --> 30:11.250
is repairing roads.

30:11.250 --> 30:12.050
You must be very busy.

30:12.050 --> 30:12.850
You took time

30:12.920 --> 30:13.770
out of your busy schedule

30:13.770 --> 30:14.440
to meet us.

30:14.440 --> 30:15.290
Thank you for your trouble.

30:15.290 --> 30:16.490
They're not here yet?

30:19.850 --> 30:20.920
Tie, hurry up.

30:20.920 --> 30:22.850
We've been waiting for a long time.

30:24.610 --> 30:25.340
Feng Tieyou.

30:26.160 --> 30:28.220
Section Chief Wang, nice to meet you.

30:38.070 --> 30:40.400
Section Chief Wang, please come in. Come.

30:40.740 --> 30:43.510
-Uncle Wang, please come in.
-Section Chief Wang, how about...

30:43.510 --> 30:44.310
Sitting here?

30:47.070 --> 30:48.700
Tired from the morning meeting, huh?

30:48.700 --> 30:49.600
A bit tired.

30:54.770 --> 30:56.460
Why don't you sit back a bit?

30:56.460 --> 30:58.190
I'm afraid you might slide off.

30:58.880 --> 30:59.940
Alright. Alright.

31:00.380 --> 31:01.510
Section Chief Wang.

31:02.370 --> 31:03.150
Have a seat.

31:10.090 --> 31:11.220
Section Chief Wang.

31:11.690 --> 31:13.950
What was the meeting about this morning?

31:14.330 --> 31:16.090
Uncle Wang is my neighbor.

31:16.180 --> 31:17.110
Right next door.

31:17.920 --> 31:20.050
I'm asking what the meeting was about.

31:20.680 --> 31:21.360
Well,

31:22.290 --> 31:23.160
it's the leaders' business.

31:23.160 --> 31:23.850
Don't pry.

31:24.000 --> 31:26.200
It was an internal system work meeting.

31:26.240 --> 31:27.360
Internal system work meeting?

31:27.360 --> 31:28.440
Why are you whispering?

31:28.440 --> 31:29.840
We are in the same system.

31:30.810 --> 31:31.770
Section Chief Wang,

31:31.770 --> 31:32.270
listen,

31:32.330 --> 31:33.590
I haven't introduced myself properly.

31:33.590 --> 31:34.220
I

31:34.610 --> 31:35.700
am in engineering.

31:36.740 --> 31:38.670
We're actually in the same system.

31:38.720 --> 31:39.740
Now we know each other.

31:39.740 --> 31:40.750
Since we're acquainted now,

31:40.750 --> 31:42.010
things will be easier.

31:42.050 --> 31:43.660
If you have any instructions

31:43.660 --> 31:44.290
or anything,

31:44.290 --> 31:45.460
just come to me directly.

31:45.460 --> 31:46.400
My men

31:46.480 --> 31:47.920
can handle things smoothly.

31:47.920 --> 31:48.540
Right.

31:58.750 --> 32:01.940
When I first took office,

32:03.920 --> 32:05.890
Luo's hostel

32:06.680 --> 32:07.550
was expanding.

32:09.500 --> 32:10.660
This hostel

32:11.050 --> 32:13.460
has my blood, sweat, and tears.

32:14.980 --> 32:17.110
I get it. Your blood, sweat, and tears.

32:17.790 --> 32:20.050
Section Chief Wang, you're from He'nan?

32:20.740 --> 32:22.070
Isn't he your neighbor?

32:22.200 --> 32:23.270
You're from He'nan too?

32:23.270 --> 32:23.790
No, I...

32:24.460 --> 32:25.210
Well,

32:25.460 --> 32:26.520
Section Chief Wang

32:26.550 --> 32:27.750
lived with his grandparents

32:27.750 --> 32:28.640
since childhood.

32:28.640 --> 32:29.830
It's hard to change a local accent.

32:29.830 --> 32:30.400
Right.

32:30.980 --> 32:33.610
Uncle Wang's ancestral home is He'nan.

32:34.420 --> 32:35.200
Feng.

32:35.870 --> 32:36.460
Don't interrupt.

32:36.460 --> 32:38.190
Let Section Chief Wang finish.

32:43.850 --> 32:44.480
Well,

32:49.050 --> 32:49.700
you see,

32:51.400 --> 32:51.900
I...

32:52.510 --> 32:53.570
before I came here,

32:54.740 --> 32:55.790
I told Liangliang

32:56.880 --> 32:57.540
that today,

32:59.110 --> 33:00.770
we shouldn't be extravagant.

33:01.610 --> 33:02.810
It's a family dinner.

33:02.850 --> 33:04.450
Just a simple family dinner.

33:05.530 --> 33:06.050
Understood.

33:06.050 --> 33:06.450
Right.

33:07.110 --> 33:08.030
Keep it simple.

33:08.530 --> 33:08.940
Okay.

33:09.570 --> 33:10.300
Then

33:10.440 --> 33:11.220
tell the kitchen

33:11.220 --> 33:12.790
to cancel the softshell turtle.

33:12.790 --> 33:13.390
You got it.

33:13.570 --> 33:15.300
The softshell turtle is great.

33:19.790 --> 33:20.200
Great.

33:28.850 --> 33:29.980
Section Chief Wang.

33:31.350 --> 33:33.250
I heard nowadays all the leaders

33:33.270 --> 33:34.230
play golf.

33:35.530 --> 33:36.310
You play too?

33:36.460 --> 33:37.920
I see you're quite tanned.

33:39.160 --> 33:40.220
What's your score?

33:49.420 --> 33:50.280
Fifty strokes?

33:52.720 --> 33:53.400
Forty?

33:54.240 --> 33:54.760
Thir...

33:55.030 --> 33:56.180
No, it can't be lower.

33:56.180 --> 33:57.240
It's not possible.

33:58.440 --> 33:59.700
He plays 5 times a week.

34:01.030 --> 34:02.140
Five times a week?

34:02.480 --> 34:03.860
Is there time for work?

34:04.180 --> 34:05.110
Work is work,

34:05.140 --> 34:06.300
golf is golf.

34:06.440 --> 34:08.040
He plays during lunch break.

34:09.260 --> 34:11.260
During lunch break?

34:15.230 --> 34:16.610
Let's have the food served.

34:16.610 --> 34:17.170
Section Chief Wang.

34:17.170 --> 34:18.070
Let's have another drink.

34:18.070 --> 34:18.469
Drink.

34:18.530 --> 34:19.090
Bottoms up.

34:19.090 --> 34:19.400
Bottoms up.

34:19.400 --> 34:20.530
Come on, bottoms up.

34:24.030 --> 34:25.190
Come on, young man.

34:25.260 --> 34:25.860
Uncle Wang.

34:25.860 --> 34:26.820
I'll return the toast.

34:26.820 --> 34:27.400
Come on.

34:27.420 --> 34:28.380
Fine, you return the toast. Come on.

34:28.380 --> 34:28.840
Cheers.

34:28.840 --> 34:29.770
No need, no need.

34:29.820 --> 34:30.650
Enough.

34:30.760 --> 34:31.650
Come on.

34:31.880 --> 34:33.080
You can really drink.

34:33.260 --> 34:34.550
Uncle Wang, stop drinking.

34:34.550 --> 34:35.090
Have a rest.

34:35.090 --> 34:35.670
I can't drink anymore.

34:35.670 --> 34:36.409
Rest a bit.

34:36.480 --> 34:37.400
This wine is good.

34:37.400 --> 34:38.150
-Come on.
-Stop it.

34:38.150 --> 34:39.190
Let's have a drink.

34:39.190 --> 34:39.940
Why would I drink with you?

34:39.940 --> 34:40.870
Luo, come.

34:41.070 --> 34:42.520
Drink.

34:42.670 --> 34:43.530
Let's have one.

34:44.230 --> 34:46.110
-Section Chief Wang.
-This wine is good.

34:46.110 --> 34:46.699
Well,

34:46.860 --> 34:47.920
let's drink later.

34:47.980 --> 34:49.300
Tell Tie

34:49.780 --> 34:50.710
why he can't

34:50.730 --> 34:52.860
kick the regulars

34:52.900 --> 34:53.800
out of my hostel.

34:53.800 --> 34:54.270
Right.

34:55.110 --> 34:55.550
What?

34:56.500 --> 34:58.560
The regulars in my hostel

34:58.920 --> 34:59.840
can't be driven away.

34:59.840 --> 35:01.160
Okay, okay.

35:01.800 --> 35:02.360
Tie.

35:02.780 --> 35:03.650
You know what?

35:04.900 --> 35:06.290
At my unit,

35:07.090 --> 35:08.470
the young people

35:09.030 --> 35:10.220
asked me,

35:10.570 --> 35:11.210
"Boss,

35:12.340 --> 35:14.600
why do you protect

35:14.860 --> 35:16.020
Luo's

35:16.280 --> 35:17.310
inn so much?"

35:17.500 --> 35:18.530
Why?

35:18.630 --> 35:19.790
Why?

35:20.110 --> 35:20.780
I told them

35:22.170 --> 35:23.890
the young people living there

35:25.110 --> 35:25.870
were all

35:26.960 --> 35:28.000
crouching tigers

35:28.650 --> 35:29.780
and hidden dragons.

35:30.280 --> 35:30.860
Right?

35:31.960 --> 35:32.760
In the future,

35:33.170 --> 35:34.370
they will make it big.

35:34.840 --> 35:35.980
That place

35:36.170 --> 35:38.320
can be treated as a tourist spot.

35:38.710 --> 35:40.100
They can sell tickets.

35:40.460 --> 35:41.520
So,

35:42.110 --> 35:43.840
the young people in this hostel

35:44.190 --> 35:46.160
are my family.

35:46.780 --> 35:48.860
No one is allowed to move in.

35:49.050 --> 35:50.690
No one is allowed to take it.

35:51.630 --> 35:52.480
Calm down.

35:52.510 --> 35:53.610
Section Chief Wang.

35:53.610 --> 35:54.050
Tie.

35:55.000 --> 35:56.500
Do you understand my difficulties?

35:56.500 --> 35:57.300
I got it.

35:57.340 --> 35:58.000
I understand completely.

35:58.000 --> 35:59.130
Section Chief Wang.

35:59.780 --> 36:01.610
You have to stand up for us.

36:02.940 --> 36:07.570
If an official doesn't serve the people,

36:11.340 --> 36:15.710
he might as well go home
and sell sweet potatoes.

36:19.940 --> 36:24.330
I, the magistrate,

36:25.090 --> 36:29.130
laugh with joy.

36:29.400 --> 36:32.930
From a small hole, I pulled out

36:33.380 --> 36:35.780
a big crab.

36:35.800 --> 36:37.530
That's enough. That's enough.

36:38.550 --> 36:40.020
Look at this.

36:40.150 --> 36:40.530
Section Chief Wang.

36:40.530 --> 36:42.340
Isn't that strange?

36:42.550 --> 36:43.010
Enough.

36:43.030 --> 36:44.840
Who can see

36:44.840 --> 36:49.130
me, a petty seventh-rank official?

36:49.340 --> 36:51.690
I can interrogate the Madam.

36:51.840 --> 36:56.340
I don't care for your gold ingots.

36:56.340 --> 37:00.730
When you die, Madam,
I'll buy you a coffin.

37:00.780 --> 37:04.480
I'll buy you a coffin.

37:10.070 --> 37:11.090
Bravo! Bravo!

37:11.610 --> 37:12.270
Bravo!

37:14.820 --> 37:15.750
Uncle...

37:16.980 --> 37:17.780
Uncle Wang is tired.

37:17.780 --> 37:18.920
I'm tired. I'm tired.

37:18.920 --> 37:19.910
Rest a bit.

37:26.050 --> 37:26.530
Bravo!

37:27.210 --> 37:27.690
Bravo!

37:28.300 --> 37:28.760
Bravo!

37:29.820 --> 37:30.480
Backswing.

37:31.980 --> 37:32.510
Swing.

37:34.050 --> 37:34.710
Watch it go.

37:36.090 --> 37:37.070
Now that is golf.

37:37.130 --> 37:37.690
You know?

37:39.800 --> 37:40.630
Look at you.

37:42.440 --> 37:43.580
Feet apart.

37:43.900 --> 37:45.030
Stick your butt out.

37:48.810 --> 37:50.300
You think I'm not talking to you?

37:50.300 --> 37:51.200
Feet apart.

37:55.260 --> 37:56.910
We've had food and drinks.

37:56.940 --> 37:57.800
I paid the bill.

37:58.550 --> 38:00.210
I've seen enough of this show.

38:01.670 --> 38:03.530
It hasn't been easy for you three.

38:04.210 --> 38:05.610
Little Northeasterner.

38:06.690 --> 38:08.640
You're playing tricks on me.

38:08.760 --> 38:09.360
Acting.

38:10.110 --> 38:10.550
Let me tell you.

38:10.550 --> 38:11.400
I'll go to

38:11.420 --> 38:13.080
your little hostel tomorrow.

38:13.510 --> 38:14.710
If you don't sign the contract,

38:14.710 --> 38:15.730
I'll tear it down.

38:18.070 --> 38:19.600
Section Chief Wang, right?

38:20.940 --> 38:22.800
Why are you dodging? Come closer.

38:23.210 --> 38:25.570
You sing He'nan Opera well. Not bad.

38:26.500 --> 38:27.700
Put your glasses on.

38:27.800 --> 38:29.280
I can't stand that darn face of yours.

38:29.280 --> 38:29.730
I wasn't talking about you.

38:29.730 --> 38:30.930
Put the glasses down.

38:31.860 --> 38:32.590
Stop acting.

38:35.050 --> 38:36.230
Aren't you a neighbor?

38:36.230 --> 38:37.210
Where are you from?

38:37.210 --> 38:37.730
Zhengzhou.

38:37.730 --> 38:38.510
No, Xuanwu.

38:42.090 --> 38:43.090
Look at you all.

38:43.300 --> 38:44.440
Act. Keep acting.

38:46.130 --> 38:46.840
Watch them.

38:46.890 --> 38:47.750
Make them play.

38:47.920 --> 38:48.870
Keep playing.

38:48.900 --> 38:50.030
Until they can't lift their chopsticks.

38:50.030 --> 38:51.030
That's when they stop.

38:51.030 --> 38:52.030
Don't worry, bro.

38:53.760 --> 38:54.420
Backswing.

38:55.640 --> 38:56.390
Swing.

38:57.280 --> 38:57.940
Watch it go.

38:59.260 --> 38:59.920
Backswing.

39:01.380 --> 39:02.000
Swing.

39:03.050 --> 39:03.710
Watch it go.

39:08.360 --> 39:09.440
This is

39:10.650 --> 39:11.710
a nightmare.

39:13.130 --> 39:13.710
Mr. Tao.

39:13.780 --> 39:14.860
Take a break.

39:15.280 --> 39:16.710
Haven't you played enough?

39:16.710 --> 39:17.920
I have to master

39:17.920 --> 39:18.900
this technique.

39:19.110 --> 39:21.440
Otherwise, I suffered for nothing today.

39:22.380 --> 39:23.420
I'm telling you two,

39:23.420 --> 39:24.840
don't tell anyone about this.

39:24.840 --> 39:25.800
Take it to the grave.

39:25.800 --> 39:27.920
That meal was so embarrassing.

39:29.860 --> 39:30.790
You're all back.

39:31.850 --> 39:33.710
What did you eat to get this drunk?

39:33.840 --> 39:35.170
Did you get the job done?

39:36.300 --> 39:37.030
We seemed to

39:39.030 --> 39:40.690
be eating a softshell turtle.

39:41.210 --> 39:42.340
A softshell turtle?

39:43.530 --> 39:44.720
You ate quite well.

39:46.560 --> 39:47.560
No, I mean the job.

39:49.710 --> 39:51.010
It's really a setback.

39:52.460 --> 39:53.320
He suffered it.

39:54.090 --> 39:55.550
Can you do anything right?

40:08.150 --> 40:08.750
He's here.

40:12.530 --> 40:13.530
You're here, Bro.

40:13.800 --> 40:14.380
Everyone's here?

40:14.380 --> 40:14.670
Yes.

40:14.670 --> 40:15.050
Tie.

40:15.150 --> 40:16.410
No music?

40:18.260 --> 40:18.950
Come on.

40:19.240 --> 40:20.270
Bring the booze.

40:20.460 --> 40:21.190
Thanks, Bro.

40:23.230 --> 40:24.790
Whose girlfriend is this?

40:24.810 --> 40:25.570
The new girl.

40:26.590 --> 40:27.480
What's her name?

40:27.480 --> 40:28.030
Hui.

40:28.760 --> 40:30.220
Hurry up with the skewers.

40:30.380 --> 40:31.090
Okay.

40:36.500 --> 40:37.210
Who are you?

41:13.190 --> 41:14.190
How does it taste?

41:15.280 --> 41:15.880
It's okay.

41:17.280 --> 41:18.680
Bro, there's no one else.

41:18.820 --> 41:19.600
Just him.

41:21.690 --> 41:22.800
You've got guts, kid.

41:22.800 --> 41:23.980
Coming here alone to start trouble?

41:23.980 --> 41:25.240
Looking for a beating?

41:33.300 --> 41:35.130
I've told you everything I can.

41:36.300 --> 41:37.400
Feng Tieyou

41:38.010 --> 41:39.070
has made mistakes,

41:40.030 --> 41:41.530
but it was all for his brothers.

41:41.530 --> 41:42.780
He's all bluster.

41:43.090 --> 41:44.800
You don't need to be afraid of him.

41:44.800 --> 41:45.650
If it weren't for the child

41:45.650 --> 41:46.980
wanting to call him Dad,

41:47.670 --> 41:48.260
I wouldn't have

41:48.260 --> 41:49.660
held out any hope for him.

41:58.220 --> 41:58.820
Take this.

42:03.260 --> 42:04.920
This is as far as I can help you.

42:08.690 --> 42:09.950
Where did you get this?

42:10.180 --> 42:11.710
He's asking you a question.

42:12.690 --> 42:14.950
What's your relationship with Chen Yan?

42:15.400 --> 42:16.440
I call her Sis.

42:22.710 --> 42:23.370
Break it up.

42:27.360 --> 42:29.090
Have you seen her and the child?

42:31.260 --> 42:32.010
Did Chen Yan

42:32.710 --> 42:34.310
tell you to tell me anything?

42:38.460 --> 42:39.310
Not really.

42:42.210 --> 42:43.280
Tie, I came here

42:44.190 --> 42:45.970
for my own business.

42:47.440 --> 42:49.440
I live at the Seasons Change Hostel.

42:54.430 --> 42:55.640
Oh, that.
